title: LF Team or Players for NZGC Wildcards (MUST BE A NEW ZEALANDER)
body:
Looking for players willing to be apart of the NZGC Wildcards, they need to be from New Zealand. If you're interested DeathGod64 asap for a chance to be in a team ^_^

EDIT: Registrations close 4th December at 8PM NZST
Here is the official Facebook page.
